# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
debug
target

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# Generated by cargo mutants
# Contains mutation testing data
**/mutants.out*/

# RustRover
#  JetBrains specific template is maintained in a separate JetBrains.gitignore that can
#  be found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/JetBrains.gitignore
#  and can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file.  For a more nuclear
#  option (not recommended) you can uncomment the following to ignore the entire idea folder.
#.idea/


# CLI-specific agent instruction symlinks (symlinked to AGENTS.md)
CLAUDE.md
GEMINI.md

# AI tool configuration directories (local per-developer)
.claude/
.gemini/
.cursor/
.aider*
.codex/
.vibe/
.cline/
.clinerules/
.opencode/
.rtk/

# mdBook build output
docs/book/

# Added by cargo

/target
.git-paw/logs/
.git-paw/sessions/
.git-paw/tmp/
.git-paw/baseline-head.txt
.git-paw/baseline-summary.txt
.git-paw/baseline-test.log

# Per-worktree agent-instruction sidecar: the combined view of the project's
# AGENTS.md plus git-paw's ephemeral per-session injection. Never committed —
# the tracked AGENTS.md stays a normal committable file (finding F10).
.git-paw/AGENTS.local.md

# Project management files (not tracked)
TODO.md
MILESTONE.md

# OpenSpec archive + release-notes — gitignored from v0.5.0 onwards.
# The canonical post-archive state lives in openspec/specs/. Each
# developer's local archive view is regenerated by `openspec archive`
# during the cycle; the directories are not shared via git.
openspec/changes/archive/
openspec/changes/_release-notes/
.git-paw/session-summary.md

# Operator/monitor scratch scripts live locally under .git-paw/scripts/ but are
# NOT part of the tool — only the bundled sweep.sh (written by `git paw init`
# from assets/scripts/sweep.sh) is tracked here. (v0.8.0 will fold the monitor
# logic into `git paw start --unattended`.)
.git-paw/scripts/*
!.git-paw/scripts/sweep.sh

# Root-level operator scratch logs (drive/sweep/verify/docbuild/baseline runs)
.git-paw/*.log
.git-paw/session-learnings.md
.git-paw/worktrees/
